{"tid":1837862,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】內地訪港旅客指報道太誇張：「武漢的同學」都沒有戴口罩","createTime":"2020-01-23T20:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T17:16:19.000Z","uid":226548,"like":9,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"54beb39082abd148404a7e6a7d353dcd0a8c28fb","tid":1837862,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3884748/org/ca80e16f6ad1b8003d9900f58c8805b4.jpg/6SPaXvVB96i_RCm76bFr17EZcNxiU9zcKQToxykE6Mc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3884748%2Forg%2Fca80e16f6ad1b8003d9900f58c8805b4.jpg%2F6SPaXvVB96i_RCm76bFr17EZcNxiU9zcKQToxykE6Mc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=3866eced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢爆發不明肺炎疫情，國家衛健委確認廣東省首宗輸入性新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎確診病例，患者為一名現居深圳的66歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n不過，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有來港購物的深圳旅客稱不擔心疫情</span></strong>，又指朋友圈未有於社交平台討論事件，反而覺得新聞報道太誇張：「我武漢的同學都沒有戴口罩。」有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">內地旅客亦認為，當年沙士「也是這樣過來，沒什麼好怕。」</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e65317f80734e8c68b85190e41939b473cd1946a","tid":1837862,"uid":146877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da5de751acf28890b0c04d0cd757fcfb6bddf92","tid":1837862,"uid":226548,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:32:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>深圳旅客：媒體說得很誇張</strong><br />\n<br />\n來自深圳的旅客劉小姐指，每個月來港兩次，直言不太了解武漢肺炎疫情，指「我們那裏（深圳）沒病毒，沒聽說這些，我們正常生活！」經記者告知後，她始知深圳有一宗確診案例，劉說自己的生活圈子沒這些病人，不擔心疫情，更展示微信朋友圈予記者看：「都是出去玩的、發廣告的！」<br />\n<br />\n劉小姐認為，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢肺炎疫情沒媒體說得那麼誇張</span></strong>，「新聞說得很嚴重，但人家還是該生活的該生活，我武漢的同學都沒有戴口罩！」<br />\n<br />\n另一位來自<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">深圳的旅客姚小姐則反問記者：「有什麼好怕？」</span></strong>她更舉例2003年爆發沙士疫情，「也是這樣過來」，認為當時疫情不是很嚴重，「該上班上班，該下班下班，該坐車坐車，生活如常呀。」她又指自己當年都沒戴口罩。她又指，不了解深圳有確診個案，微信朋友圈、微博都沒有人在議論。"},{"pid":"23a4b958ac6a513245e8437b9c8dbc56f39f5b70","tid":1837862,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:33:15.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/424119/武漢肺炎-深圳訪港旅客指報道太誇張-武漢的同學都沒有戴口罩\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F424119%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E6%8C%87%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E5%A4%AA%E8%AA%87%E5%BC%B5-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E9%83%BD%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=0a1c8bba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/424119/武漢肺炎-深圳訪港旅客指報道太誇張-武漢的同學都沒有戴口罩</a>"},{"pid":"5f70b7986566e43821a4157e90379f39347be67f","tid":1837862,"uid":198035,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:34:07.000Z","msg":"死返上去啦 dklm"},{"pid":"01db5f0e9ecbe3006db71c192f0fb90aa81eda49","tid":1837862,"uid":88743,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fL9QPaL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfL9QPaL.gif&h=d3ca1323&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8a4d1b7e9a67089a2f3ec4129378e7d9a21a4d8","tid":1837862,"uid":165361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:36:26.000Z","msg":"你又知你個&quot;武漢的同學&quot; 無中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94e6986aba0c08bd0d9f13260f6d19432e3e546","tid":1837862,"uid":88743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:38:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2020-01-20 16:41<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-01-20 19:25</span></span></strong><br />\n今日問佢地唔知會有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/